                                <tls:srcline title="劉義慶世說新語" target="#KR3l0002_tls_023-27a.3" pos="3">卞令禮法自居。</tls:srcline>
                                <tls:line title="劉義慶世說新語 (en)" src="Mather">whereas Biàn Kǔn 壼 always kept himself within the bounds of propriety and law.</tls:line>
